Source: pg-variables
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/postgrespro/pg_variables

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-variables
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-variables
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Session-scoped variables with scalar, array, and record types
  pg_variables provides session-wide PostgreSQL variables of scalar, array,
  and record types, with optional transactional behavior.
